Adminer is a full-featured database management tool written in PHP. It is a lightweight and more efficient alternative to phpMyAdmin. 

Adminer provides a user-friendly interface for managing databases, tables, columns, relations, indexes, users, permissions, and more. It supports a wide range of databases including MySQL, PostgreSQL, SQLite, MS SQL, Oracle, and others.

You can use Adminer to perform tasks such as:

- Creating, editing, and deleting databases and tables
- Executing SQL queries
- Managing users and permissions
- Importing and exporting data in various formats

Adminer is available as a single PHP file which can be uploaded to your server and accessed via a web browser. It's also available as a Docker image, which can be useful in development environments.

